---
title: Quick Char Siu Beef Strips Noodle Stir-Fry with Capsicum & Sesame Seeds
description: Time to get saucy tonight with a stir-fry. Not only is this beef strips udon bowl chock-full of colour, flavour and texture, it comes together in four simple steps, so you'll be slurping your way to bliss in no time.
